### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
### English Learning App — API Smoke Test
### Chạy bằng VS Code REST Client extension (humao.rest-client)
### Docs đầy đủ: ../docs/API-CONTRACTS.md
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

@baseUrl = https://english-admin-websites-production.up.railway.app/api/v1
@contentType = application/json

